# Didactic Resources
:res_skiena_manual_1 a guide:DidacticResource ;
    guide:bibliographyTitle "The Algorithm Design Manual" ;
    guide:bibliographyDescription "Steven S. Skiena. The Algorithm Design Manual. Springer, London, 2008." ;
    guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .

:res_skschema_manual_2 a guide:DidacticResource ;
    guide:bibliographyTitle "Programming Challenges: The Programming Contest Training Manual" ;
    guide:bibliographyDescription "Steven S. Skiena and Miguel Revilla. Springer-Verlag, 2003." ;
    guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .

:res_knuth_vol3 a guide:DidacticResource ;
    guide:bibliographyTitle "The Art of Computer Programming, Volume 3: (2nd Ed.) Sorting and Searching" ;
    guide:bibliographyDescription "Donald E. Knuth. Addison Wesley Longman Publishing Co., Inc., USA, 1998." ;
    guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .

:res_knuth_part1 a guide:DidacticResource ;
    guide:bibliographyTitle "The Art of Computer Programming: Combinatorial Algorithms, Part 1" ;
    guide:bibliographyDescription "Donald E. Knuth. Addison-Wesley Professional, 2011." ;
    guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .

:res_laaksonen_guide a guide:DidacticResource ;
    guide:bibliographyTitle "Guide to Competitive Programming: Learning and Improving Algorithms Through Contests" ;
    guide:bibliographyDescription "Antti Laaksonen. Springer Verlag, 2017." ;
    guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .